### Create Asset bundle
POST http://localhost:8080/assets/bundles
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Token: root

{
  "identifier": "weekly-pack-03",
  "assets": [
    { "text": "X: Rare", "totalSupply": 11 },
    { "text": "E: Epic", "totalSupply": 4 }
  ]
}

